tiers.ability_description: Whenever Dark Side allies inflict a debuff, they gain 2% Critical Chance (stacking) for 3 turns.
Whenever First Order allies Stun an enemy, they gain Speed Up and Offense Up for 2 turns and inflict Expose for 2 turns at the end of that turn, which can't be evaded.
At the start of Kylo Ren (Unmasked)'s turn, dispel all debuffs on them. They recover 5% Health for each debuff dispelled this way.
Whenever Light Side allies use a Special ability, they gain Evasion Up, Health Steal Up, and Health Up  for 2 turns.
Whenever enemies are damaged at the start of their turn, Unaligned Force User allies gain 2% Turn Meter.
Whenever Ben Solo deals damage to an enemy, remove 25% Turn Meter from that enemy.
Whenever Light Side allies are evaded by an enemy, that ally gains Accuracy Up for 2 turns, and they inflict Evasion Down for 2 turns on that enemy, which can't be evaded.
Light Side allies have +100% Critical Chance while attacking out of turn.
At the start of each Rogue One ally's turn, if they have not taken damage since their last turn, they gain Critical Chance Up and Offense Up for 1 turn.
Whenever Jyn Erso critically hits an enemy, Jyn Erso gains 10% Critical Damage, Defense Penetration, and Offense (stacking, max 200%) until the end of battle.
At the beginning of their turn, Light Side allies have +25% chance to dispel all debuffs on themself.
Whenever Attacker allies use a Special Ability on their turn, they gain Riposte for 2 turns.

Whenever Resistance Trooper uses his Basic ability on his turn, he Exposes the target enemy for 2 turns. Whenever Resistance Trooper attacks an Exposed enemy, all other allies gain 20% Turn Meter, Resistance Trooper has a 50% chance to attack again and Expose a random enemy for 1 turn.

Whenever Resistance Trooper falls below 50% for the first time, he gains Damage Immunity and Health Steal Up for 2 turns and all other allies gain Evasion Up for 2 turns.
